，我们将向慈善事业和活动支付超过 370 万英镑。”</p><p>最新消息还确认，除了 370 万英镑之外，格拉斯顿伯里还通过<a href="https://www.oxfam.org.uk/media/press-releases/glastonbury-fans-have-chance-to-win-festival-tickets-by-supporting-dec-turkey-syria-earthquake-appeal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乐施会众筹 DEC 呼吁</a>筹集了超过 100 万英镑用于叙利亚-土耳其地震应对工作。</p><p>早在2月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-win-tickets-supporting-dec-turkey-syria-earthquake-appeal-3399163">音乐节就捐赠了10对门票，为呼吁筹集资金</a>。粉丝们每次参加筹款活动只需支付 10 英镑，就有机会赢得各种体验。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-auction-off-tickets-and-once-in-a-lifetime-opportunities-for-trussell-trust-3393171">Glasto 还拍卖了门票和各种“千载难逢的机会”，以帮助 Trussel Trust</a> 。组织者现已宣布，此次拍卖会为慈善机构筹集了 116,000 英镑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C018J-RK7Hl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="