。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-fans-react-as-tickets-sell-out-3543390">前两批门票于上个月开始发售</a>，但现已售罄。预计将于春季进行转售。</p><p>目前尚未宣布任何行动。最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-madonna-reportedly-set-to-headline-festival-3530560">有报道称麦当娜、杜阿·利帕和酷玩乐队将在明年夏天位列榜首</a>。然而，艾米丽·伊维斯随后表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-emily-eavis-says-rumours-about-headliners-untrue-3531152">，有关已确认的头条新闻的谣言是“不真实的”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/madonna-celebration-tour-review-setlist-3515338#:~:text=It's%20the%20only%20dud%20visual,dame%20both%20cherished%20and%20chastised.">在伊维斯分享了一张伦敦“庆典巡演”音乐会的</a>照片后，人们开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-think-emily-eavis-dropped-hint-about-madonna-headlining-glastonbury-2024-3515728">猜测麦当娜可能会出现在沃西农场</a>。按照目前的情况，流行女王将于 6 月推出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-madonna-play-i-love-new-york-for-the-first-time-in-15-years-as-she-kicks-off-us-leg-of-celebration-tour-3559064">她的北美演出</a>计划于 4 月结束。 </p><figure id="attachment_3461205" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3461205" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3461205" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme.jpeg" alt="2023 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节金字塔舞台的镜头" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/elton-glastonbury-nme-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3461205" class="wp-caption-